        [Orders:Ore/Platinum] 
        [Orders:Ore/Uranium] 
        [Orders:Ore/Lithium] 
        [Orders:Ore/Sulfur] 

        [Offers:Ingot/Iron] 
        [Offers:Ingot/Nickel] 
        [Offers:Ingot/Silicon] 
        [Offers:Ingot/Cobalt] 
        [Offers:Ingot/Magnesium] 
        [Offers:Ingot/Silver] 
